problems.title: Find Duplicate Elements using Hash Set
problems.description:
Problem Statement

You are given an array of N integers. Using a hash set, find all duplicate elements.
Print the duplicate elements in the order of their first repeated occurrence.
If no duplicates exist, print "No Duplicates".
problems.examples:
Sample Input
7
1 2 3 1 4 2 5

Sample Output
1
2

Explanation:
1 and 2 appear more than once. They are printed in order of when they were first found as duplicates.
hintsList: Use a set to track seen elements. If element is already in set, it's a duplicate.
Use another set to avoid reporting the same duplicate multiple times.
